Founder of Corundum Labs - Marc Claproth

Marc Claproth entered the blockchain arena in 2016, blending his digital commerce expertise with a growing interest in blockchain technologies. With a professional background spanning over nine years, Marc has worked alongside with global brands, helping to shape their digital narratives. His notable experience includes working on blockchain projects at Fox Entertainment, particularly focusing on NFTs, where he leveraged his skills to bridge traditional digital strategies with innovative blockchain applications.





I am Marc Claproth, and it is my commitment to develop technology that enhances the quality of life for others.
